<p>In Japan there seems to be strict separation of sects with governing DaiHonZan. I've read that in Vietnam there is kind of a government sanctioned body that governs all temples. </p>
<p>Has your research thus far uncovered any Zen sects other than Rinzai? And how Rinzai is Rinzai in Vietnam?</p>
